Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:10.47,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:28.97,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了像今天這樣的日子才叫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:39.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏過所有的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}戀愛笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:52.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手無策 在這深夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投無路 遵守著約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:02.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己鏡中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們不要被條框鎖住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:13.76,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:20.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告別 這種答案毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:25.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只會繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:22.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行屍走肉般走過的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:28.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}頭頂的陽光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:33.54,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何時你已經淪落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:39.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}連自己名字也都遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:43.46,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人類 為何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.13,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:51.04,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}這無盡的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:55.75,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如隨之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:56.74,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常之花
